<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="flash-n">flash <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /flæʃ/    美 /flæʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 闪光；闪现；(思想、情感的) 突现：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A <strong>flash of lightning</strong> lit up the night sky.
一道闪电照亮夜空。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>flash of anger</strong> / <strong>inspiration</strong>
怒上心头/灵感的闪现</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-u">2.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 闪光灯：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'll need flash for this shot.
拍这个镜头我需要闪光灯。</p></div>

<h4 id="3u">3.<strong>[U] 网站动画制作程序</strong></h4>
<h3 id="flash-card">flash card</h3>
<p>1.<strong>教学卡片；识字卡</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="in-like-a-flash">in / like a flash</h3>
<p>1.<strong>很快地；马上：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Just wait here. I'll be back in a flash.
就在这里等着，我马上回来。</p></div></div>